README:

1.) Make sure that php-cli is installed and available as /bin/php
2.) Copy all pushinfo.* files to a location that can not be accessed remotely.
3.) Install https://hg.nhg.name/unchroot/
4.) Configure pushinfo.conf.phs and make sure that all paths are accessible.
5.) Create PROCESS_USER and PROCESS_GROUP system user and system group.
6.) Set execute flag of pushinfo.phs:
    chmod +x pushinfo.sh
7.) Configure CRON to call pushinfo.phs regularly:
    */5 * * * * root /path/to/pushinfo.phs >/dev/null 2>&1
